{
  "stem": "7094.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So this was a time where I was thawing out, and it was a very black period.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You would think that having two small babies, that this will give me a pivot and strength and it will occupy me.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It did in one way, but another way, it also realized the gap and the emptiness and missing the family.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, you know, bringing up children without a grandmother, without aunt, without cousin, it created some problems, too.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And also, we were very poor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We struggled this all together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I had a sort of emotional vomiting, at that time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Obviously it had to come out one way or another.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I had a very nice psychiatrist who-- an outpatient-- and he recommended psychoanalysis.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But psychoanalysis depend-- you have to pay for it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "This is the relationship.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I couldn't afford it, so I dropped it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But he was very supportive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But there was a history of that going on in the background, all the time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I really started recovering more when I started working, because there, again, I had a discipline.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I had an order from-- I had to do certain things.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I had to be time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I didn't-- I didn't qualify in anything, so I didn't have an entrance anywhere.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But I managed to get a local job with a local store.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And very soon, within a very short time, I got a buyership, which usually takes years.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But I managed to do it within the year.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I had an interesting career, in a way, because it was local.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I lived locally.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I worked local-- I mean, I lived in Sutton, by that time-- from Morden to Sutton.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "The job in Sutton.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I could combine the job with being a mother, a wife, and a career.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
